<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:24px;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">1.<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">       </span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%;">机电耦合系统：</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:29px;line-height:150%"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;">随着科学技术的发展，在生活中或工程中，机械运动和电磁现象相互耦合的情况普遍存在。以最常见的扬声器为例，电流的输入改变了线圈的电感，产生磁力使膜片振动，膜片的位移通过电流变化对线圈施加负反馈以防止啸叫。位移和电磁在扬声器的运动过程里相互耦合。在电机、电讯、仪表、自动控制等部门里，由机械元件和电磁元件组成的系统更为普遍。对这种机电系统的数学建模需要应用力学和电磁学的综合知识。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:29px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;">1788 年，法国数学家拉格朗日（Lagrange,J.L）建立的拉格朗日方程奠定了分析力学基础（图 1）。拉格朗日方程的一般形式为</span></p><p style="text-align: center;">                             <img src="https://cors.zfour.workers.dev/?http://image.sciencenet.cn/home/202111/03/085103l8383tz7811t08p1.png" title alt="机电1.png" width="425" height="76" style="width: 425px; height: 76px;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">                              <span style="font-family: "times new roman";">(1)</span><br></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;">其中 </span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em><span style="line-height: 150%;">q<sub>j  </sub></span></em><span style="line-height: 150%;">(<em>j </em>= 1,2,···, <em>f</em>)</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;"> 为广义坐标，</span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em><span style="line-height: 150%;">T</span></em></span><em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;"> </span></em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;">和 </span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em><span style="line-height: 150%;">V</span></em></span><em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;"> </span></em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;">为机械系统的动能和势能，</span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em><span style="line-height: 150%;">Ψ<sub>q</sub></span></em></span><em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;"><sub> </sub></span></em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;">为瑞利耗散函数，</span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em><span style="line-height: 150%;">Q<sub>j</sub></span></em></span><em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;"><sub> </sub></span></em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;">为广义力。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt width="325" height="346" style="width: 325px; height: 346px;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span></p><p style="text-align:center;text-indent:29px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;">图1  拉格朗日（Lagrange,J.L, 1736-1813）</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;">百年后苏格兰物理学家麦克斯韦 (Maxwell,J.C.) 于 1865 年发表了描述电磁运动普遍规律的麦克斯韦(Maxwell,J.C.) 方程，奠定了电磁学的理论基础（图 2）。机电系统动力学的数学模型由这两类方程耦合构成。拉格朗日方程是理工科大学理论力学课程的主要内容之一，其推导过程已在课程中阐明。以下仅对麦克斯韦方程做简要说明。</span></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt width="307" height="349" style="width: 307px;
